message.text:
𝐓𝐨 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐯𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐧𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐜𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐥𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐩 — 𝐇𝐚𝐩𝐩𝐲 𝐁𝐢𝐫𝐭𝐡𝐝𝐚𝐲, 𝐕𝐢𝐞𝐥! 🌍✨

Through your commitment to building bridges and fostering partnerships, you have strengthened the bonds that make our community thrive. 

Your passion for service and resilience in leadership continue to shine as an inspiration to everyone in the FEU College Y Club.

To our 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐄𝐱𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐧𝐚𝐥 𝐀𝐟𝐟𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐬, 𝐕𝐢𝐞𝐥 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐫 𝐂𝐚𝐛𝐫𝐞𝐫𝐨𝐬, we celebrate you today with gratitude and admiration. May this new year of life bring greater opportunities, endless joy, and the fulfillment of your dreams. 💚

#DefyingLimits
#TheLegaCYContinues
#CYC27

Caption byAlexine Medenilla
Pubmat by Paula Ortiz, Janelle Tañedo

message.text:
𝐓𝐨 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐯𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐧𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐜𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐥𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐩 — 𝐇𝐚𝐩𝐩𝐲 𝐁𝐢𝐫𝐭𝐡𝐝𝐚𝐲, 𝐕𝐢𝐞𝐥! 🌍✨

Your passion for service and resilience in leadership continue to shine as an inspiration to everyone in the FEU College Y Club.

To our 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐄𝐱𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐧𝐚𝐥 𝐀𝐟𝐟𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐬, 𝐕𝐢𝐞𝐥 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐫 𝐂𝐚𝐛𝐫𝐞𝐫𝐨𝐬, we celebrate you today with gratitude and admiration. May this new year of life bring greater opportunities, endless joy, and the fulfillment of your dreams. 💚

#DefyingLimits
#TheLegaCYContinues
#CYC27

Caption byAlexine Medenilla
Pubmat by Paula Ortiz, Janelle Tañedo

message.text:
𝐓𝐨 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐯𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐧𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐜𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐥𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐩 — 𝐇𝐚𝐩𝐩𝐲 𝐁𝐢𝐫𝐭𝐡𝐝𝐚𝐲, 𝐕𝐢𝐞𝐥! 🌍✨

Through your commitment to building bridges and fostering partnerships, you have strengthened the bonds that make our community thrive. 

Your passion for service and resilience in leadership continue to shine as an inspiration to everyone in the FEU College Y Club.

To our 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐄𝐱𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐧𝐚𝐥 𝐀𝐟𝐟𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐬, 𝐕𝐢𝐞𝐥 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐫 𝐂𝐚𝐛𝐫𝐞𝐫𝐨𝐬, we celebrate you today with gratitude and admiration. May this new year of life bring greater opportunities, endless joy, and the fulfillment of your dreams. 💚

#DefyingLimits
#TheLegaCYContinues
#CYC27

Caption byAlexine Medenilla
Pubmat by Paula Ortiz, Janelle Tañedo
